PrecisAppointment of JAMES WATERS, of Huntsville, Ontario, BERZOOR K. POPATIA, of Toronto, Ontario and SHIRLEY R. WALES, of London, Ontario, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years and nine months, effective August 4, 1997.
